ire a group of 8 or holding a spot for a particular class (healer and CC for instance): dying repeatedly isn't much fun <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   My goal is to minimize holding spots as much as possible.  My 2 priorities when organizing these events is 1) all participants have fun and 2) if you're in the guild you qualify for the event.<br><br>So keep watching the boards and send me any suggestions for future events or how to make improvements to the events.<br>Scottcm@usa.net<br><br>Lunasea/Sykosis/Demented/Littleboy Inmytrunk <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6B8E23><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/usareshft.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Saresh FT</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#5F9EA0>(5/2/02 12:13:35 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthforeignlegiongeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1104.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Events what's in store</span><hr size=1> Very cool Luna!  I want to thank you for doing this.  I'm not good for pulling things like this together but I like them very much!<br><br>Keep up the awesome ideas!!!  Promise I'll be home soon to participate! <p><BR>Saresh  LvL 35 Infiltrator<BR>Numms  LvL 12 Cleric<BR>Miradia  LvL 13 Wizardess<BR>Forgotten Truth (Palomides)<BR><BR>"Persistence is the key to being a true bastard."<BR>~Khaja</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub10.ezboard.com/ugizzifurrfoot.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gizzi Furrfoot</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#5F9EA0>(5/2/02 4:53:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub10.ezboard.com/fforgottentruthfor